  m_TableData:
  - m_Id: 3727839232
    m_Localized: A slime wants to teach you fight.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2473219628924928
    m_Localized: This well-trained slime won't go down so easily.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3950847510474752
    m_Localized: Normally it doesn't hurt when slimes hit you...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3964217873690624
    m_Localized: Fission seems to be the privilege of slimes.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14868905689264128
    m_Localized: Its whole body is stomach.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14869400143179776
    m_Localized: He just learned how to swing a sword......
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 16942725191348224
    m_Localized: A ninja who trained his basics well.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 17052557642739712
    m_Localized: In one sense he is well prepared.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 19810632591601664
    m_Localized: They are happy to have a training match with you.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 19810425896300544
    m_Localized: When you walk to him, he is still patting his dog.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24857606169448448
    m_Localized: 'They were also playing before they invited you. '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  references:
    version: 2
    RefIds: []
